Kenzo shaken awake by the untimely com link.  He fell out of his chair
knocking some papers off the table as he fell.
"Urr..r-roger that!"  He replied quickly.  He grabbed the papers up
off the floor and put them back onto the desk and pushed the chair in
and dashed towards Rodimus's office.  When he arrived he let himself in.
"Kenzo here."
